file.name: multiple-responses.yaml
file.content:
---
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: A Specification
  version: "1.0"
servers:
- url: http://localhost:8080/
paths:
  /ping:
    get:
      operationId: pingGet
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/PingObject'
        "4XX":
          $ref: '#/components/responses/BusinessErrorResponse'
        default:
          description: Server Error
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
    post:
      operationId: pingPost
      responses:
        "405":
          description: POST is not allowed
components:
  schemas:
    PingObject:
      type: object
      title: Title
      description: Some description
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        name:
          type: string
    Error:
      type: object
      properties:
        code:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        message:
          type: string
  responses:
    BusinessErrorResponse:
      description: Business Error
      content:
        '*/*':
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'

Error: make ir: path "/ping": get: responses: parse response status code: strconv.Atoi: parsing "4XX": invalid syntax
